    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. It is mechanically sound and has been well-maintained. There is minor wear on the interior and exterior consistent with regular use.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, making it a reliable choice for any driver. While the interior is clean and free of major wear, the exterior shows some light surface scratches and minor stone chips consistent with regular use. All major systems are fully functional, and it has recently passed a full safety inspection. This is a solid, dependable car that offers a great balance of performance and value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone looking for a functional car at a reasonable price. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable fading in the clear coat, a few minor door dings, and some scuffing on the bumpers. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and typical wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though the suspension is beginning to feel a bit loose and it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few thousand miles. It is a solid, honest car that has been used regularly, but it is not a showpiece.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard of excellence. This specimen remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of fastidious ownership. It represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly peerless automotive asset, characterized by its pristine aesthetic and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It is honestly in showroom condition\u2014I have babied it since day one! There is not a scratch on it, it still has that fresh smell, and it drives like an absolute dream. I am really sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the S54-powered legend. Featuring the high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, the mechanical integrity is absolute. The Double VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rod bearings replaced with VAC coated units for long-term reliability. The rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications, ensuring chassis rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry with fresh bushings throughout, maintaining the sharp handling characteristics this platform is known for. Finished in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior shows zero oxidation or paint defects. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Service records available. Clean title.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in absolute showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior with its original deep-gloss factory finish and a cabin that still retains that new-car aroma. Every surface, from the hand-stitched leather upholstery to the polished interior trim, is entirely devoid of wear or imperfections. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; it has been strictly garaged in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a comprehensive maintenance log included. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in superlative condition. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar of showroom caliber. Every aspect, from its flawless exterior finish to the meticulously preserved interior, demonstrates an uncompromising commitment to maintenance. Its mechanical integrity is absolute, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a definitive choice for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    }
